==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Novatian
<hw>No*va"tian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld>
<def>One of the sect of <etsep>Novatius</etsep>, or
<etsep>Novatianus</etsep>, who held that the lapsed might not be
received again into communion with the church, and that second marriages
are unlawful.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Novatianism</ent>⟦br⟧
